        </li>
        <li>
          “Sometimes I get a bike or scooter that dies on me, so I end up taking
          a car anyway, which defeats the purpose of trying to reduce my carbon
          footprint and save money.”
        </li>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-teal-200">
        <h2 class="text-unicycleSecondary">Thinks</h2>
        <li>
          Micro-mobility options are a great way to incorporate exercise into
          travel, so he doesn’t have to carve out dedicated time in his
          schedule.
        </li>
        <li>
          It’s unfortunate that micro-mobility options are not very functional
          during the winter months.
        </li>
        <li>
          It would be nice if he could plan a route that is customized for
          micro-mobility options so he feels prepared to embark on his trip.
        </li>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-unicycleSecondary/80 text-white">
        <h2 class="text-unicyclePrimary">Does</h2>
        <li>Commutes between three boroughs for school, work, and home</li>
        <li>
